message:
Inauguration of the Afghanistan India Friendship Dam is a historic moment of emotion & pride in the relations between Afghanistan and India. This is a project that will irrigate lands & light up homes. The dam is a generator of optimism & belief in the future of Afghanistan.

The brave Afghan people are sending a strong message that the forces of destruction & death, denial and domination, shall not prevail. India cherishes the friendship with Afghanistan. In Afghanistan, we want to see democracy strike deep roots, people unite & economy prosper.

Today, we are reviving a region, restoring hope, renewing life and redefining Afghanistan’s future. http://nm-4.com/u5iq
